### ============================================================================
### TEST 5: Error Handling Tests
### ============================================================================

### 5.1 Invalid bang shortcut (should return 400)
POST http://localhost:8000/web-search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "test query",
  "bang": "!invalid_bang",
  "language": "en"
}

### 5.2 Invalid category (should return error in response)
POST http://localhost:8000/web-search/specialized
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "test query",
  "category": "invalid_category",
  "language": "en"
}

### 5.3 Invalid time range (should return error)
POST http://localhost:8000/web-search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "test query",
  "time_range": "invalid_range",
  "language": "en"
}

### 5.4 Page out of range (should still work but return fewer results)
POST http://localhost:8000/web-search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "test",
  "page": 1000,
  "per_page": 10
}

### 5.5 Per page exceeds maximum (should error or limit to 100)
POST http://localhost:8000/web-search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "test",
  "per_page": 1000
}
